title: My favourite messenger!
text: If you are invited to channels with child porn and so on, it is primarily your fault, not the developer's. I have been using this messenger since its creation and have never encountered anything like this. If yours is buggy, it’s again your fault, because you were stingy to buy a normal phone. If you are a person with normal interests, a good phone and love privacy, then these are the apps for you, don’t listen to others, draw your own conclusions.

title: Error message
